          </p>

          <p class="pt-3 ">
            If your child is under 6 years old, you will have various summer camping opportunities at Siddhanta Intellectual School. Our summer camp overview for young campers who miss kindergarten or are about to go to kindergarten is a selection of the many different activities. Here are some fun summer camp activities:
          </p>

          <ul>
            <li>Magic Mania</li>
            <li>Cunning Clay</li>
            <li>Yoga and Zumba</li>
            <li>Music and Dance</li>
            <li>Making Dolls</li>
            <li>Exciting Game</li>
            <li>Creative Craftsmanship</li>
            <li>Vegetable Sculpture</li>
            <li>Flower Arrangement</li>
